    <item>
      <title>泽伦斯基描述了加入欧盟工作的近期目标</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/zelenskiy-describes-immediate-goals-work-eu-accession-2023-12-17/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总统泽伦斯基周日表示，乌克兰和欧盟委员会将很快评估基辅在将其立法与欧盟立法相一致方面取得的进展，预计将于春季制定入盟谈判框架。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/zelenskiy-describes-immediate-goals-work-eu-accession-2023-12-17/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 19:15:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>智利人拒绝用保守宪法取代独裁时代的文本</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/chileans-head-polls-again-replace-dictatorship-era-constitution-2023-12-17/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周日，智利人拒绝了一部新的保守派宪法，以取代可追溯到奥古斯托·皮诺切特独裁统治时期的现行文本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/chileans-head-polls-again-replace-dictatorship-era-constitution-2023-12-17/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 09:01:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>塞尔维亚执政党SNS将赢得选举，武契奇宣布胜利</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/serbians-vote-snap-election-ruling-party-set-secure-another-term-2023-12-17/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周日，总统亚历山大·武契奇宣布在提前举行的议会选举中获胜，此前民调机构预测其执政的塞尔维亚进步党（SNS）有望轻松获胜。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/serbians-vote-snap-election-ruling-party-set-secure-another-term-2023-12-17/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 01:04:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列开放通往加沙的援助过境点，同时加强轰炸</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/us-stresses-safety-gaza-civilians-israel-unrelenting-attacks-2023-12-15/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周日，以色列在与哈马斯长达两个多月的战争中首次开放了直接进入加沙的援助通道，但也加大了对巴勒斯坦飞地的攻击力度，称军事压力是释放人质的唯一途径。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/us-stresses-safety-gaza-civilians-israel-unrelenting-attacks-2023-12-15/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 00:45:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
